@startuml overview

left to right direction
skinparam linetype ortho

rectangle "<<Process>>\nLogging Client" as LoggingClient {
  component "mw::log\n\nDatarouterBackend" as Backend {
    component "mw::com::Receiver" as Receiver
  }
}

rectangle "<<Process>>\nDatarouter" as Datarouter {
  component "mw::com::Sender" as Sender
}

rectangle "Shared Memory" as SharedMemory

LoggingClient *-down- SharedMemory
Datarouter -down-> SharedMemory

note top of Receiver
  Instantiates side channel to receive messages from:
  /logging.<app>.<pid>.<timestamp>
end note

note right of Sender
  Creates a Sender
  Sends messages to the client via side channel
end note

Receiver -0)- Sender

note bottom of SharedMemory
  LoggingClient creates and writes to:
  /tmp/<app>.<pid>.<timestamp>.shmem
  permissions: rw-r--r--

  Datarouter discovers and opens read-only
end note

@enduml
